dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Avenal Gap quadrangle, Kings and Kern Counties, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Avenal Gap, CA 1954, Photorevised 1973, AMS 2055 IV SW - Series V895." "First printing, November 2006." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology. Includes "pertinent references."
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
